<div class="row w-100 m-0" style="overflow: hidden">
	<div id="section-main" class="sermons-col-left bg-grey" style="width:100%">
		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">第83屆 奮興會 第3講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/6">鮑維均牧師</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=83">第83屆</a>
				</span>
				<span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="性質">
					<i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>
					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=83#session-master-43">奮興會</a>
				</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="article-tag">
				<a href="#" class="badge">路加福音</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">講道會</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">56屆</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">麥希真牧師</a>
			</div>-->
			<div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
				<h2 class="article-title mb-0 h3">
					第三講  福與禍				</h2>
									<a type="button" class="bookmark ms-3 " data-model="app\models\SessionMessage" data-model-id="803"></a>
							</div>
						<div class="article-content">
				
				<div class="h5 mb-4 d-md-flex justify-content-lg-between align-items-center">
					<div><span>經文：</span> 撒母耳記上  <a class="article-citation" href="javascript:void(0)" data-book="9" data-start-chapter="3" data-start-verse="1" data-end-verse="18">3:1-18</a></div><div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-danger btn-show-scripture text-center my-2 ml-auto align-self-start" style="display:none;">顯示經文</a>
				</div></div>				<div class="WordSection1">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">在舊約聖經的人物裏面，究竟誰的童年最可憐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">呢？是摩西？約瑟？不！相信是撒母耳，我們今天先由撒母耳的童年說起。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.9pt; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">撒上三：</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">1-18<span style="letter-spacing:.05pt"> ，神作出對撒母耳的呼召，那時</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">撒母耳已經全時間奉獻給神，他從兩、三歲就在聖殿長大，撒母耳已經是神全時間的工人，那神呼召撒母耳去做甚麼呢？這是個罕有的呼召。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">這呼召是舊約聖經歷史的一個轉捩點。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.5pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-right:20.5pt; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">這故事甚至可以媲美亞伯拉罕的故事。<strong>亞伯拉</strong></span></span></span></span><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">罕，以撒，雅各三個人的太太都不能生育，如果一個不能生育，可說是意外，但三個都如此時，表明整個開始是基於恩典而不是基於人為，</span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">到撒母耳記上，同一個主題出現了。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.6pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.15pt"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Meiryo,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">聖殿中孤單成長</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:9.65pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">撒母耳的母親哈拿不能夠生育，神改變這家庭的命運，代表要改變整個以色列家的命運，一個新的、重要的時代的開始。路一：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">5-25說到撒迦利亞和以利</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">沙伯，他們在神面前是義人，只是沒有孩子，當他們</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">靠神得了兒子，表示一個新時代的開始。作者告訴我</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">們，<strong><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">在許多個時代開始時，都以不孕婦人作為主題，這不是人的作為，是神自己的工作。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.15pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.5pt; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">我是牧師的皃子，在溫馨家庭長大；撒母耳也</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">生長於類似家庭，但他並沒有溫馨可愛的童年。當時</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">的聖殿不是舒服的地方，不是所羅門所建華麗的聖</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">所，這是早期敬拜的地方，可能只是一座帳幕。一個剛斷了奶，可能才二、三歲的孩子，要離開母親，一個人在陰暗的聖殿長大，他成長是沒有母親的。撒上二：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">20說，『以利為以利加拿和他的妻祝福，說：願耶和華由這婦人再賜你後裔，代替你從耶和華求來的孩子。』試想撒母耳的父母回去後，祭司說，你父母沒有你不要緊，有第二個會代替你的。聽到會怎樣感覺？如果你自小聽到這樣的話，相信一輩子要看心理</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.2pt">專家。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.35pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.4pt; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">撒母耳從小離開了父母，以利成了他的代父，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">以利也不是個最好的祭司，當時上帝很少講話，撒母</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">耳沒聽過上帝的聲音。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">15</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">節道出撒母耳很害怕。神</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">呼召摩西、以賽亞、保羅時，神安慰他們不要害怕。 </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">17-18</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">節，「以利說：耶和華對你說甚麼，你不要向</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">我隱瞞；你若將神對你所說的隱瞞一句，願他重重的降罰與你。」撒母耳就把一切話都告訴了以利，並沒</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.25pt">有隱瞞。以利說：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.25pt">&nbsp; 這是出於耶和華，願他憑自己的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">意旨而行。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.45pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">半夜被神叫醒，神講到撒母耳惟一認識的、父親般的人，神要懲罰他，要毀滅他全家，因為他沒憑着</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">神的心意行事</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">&hellip;&hellip;撒母耳惟一依靠和尊重的人，竟如</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">此下場，這惡夢多恐怖！請問舊約聖經人物中，誰的童年最可憐？相信撒母耳榜上有名。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">自小在聖殿長大的撒母耳，已經是全時間服事</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">神的人，神現在到底要呼召他做甚麼？撒上一：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">3</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">及<span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">二：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">28</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">一再強調以利是神的祭司。如果撒母耳有個事奉的銜頭，那就應該是小祭司。『那孩子在祭司以利面前事奉耶和華。那時撒母耳還是孩子，穿着細麻布的以弗得，侍立在耶和華面前。』（撒上二：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">1</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">1</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">下， </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">18</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">）還是小孩子時已經穿着以弗得侍立在神前，雖是</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">祭司的跟班，但都是做祭司的工作。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.5pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin-right:20.6pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">三：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">1、3節說到童子撒母耳在以利面前事奉，睡在離約櫃不遠處，能在神的殿中居住，也就是神的代</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">表。那為什麼神又再呼召撒母耳呢</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">? 『耶和華又來站<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">着，像前三次呼喚說：「撒母耳阿，撒母耳阿！」撒母耳回答說：「請說，僕人敬聽。」』從</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">20節我們終於明白，這呼召使撒母耳由祭司的職分去到先知的職</span>分。在整本聖經中，第一個先知就是撒母耳 -- 『從<span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">撒母耳以來的眾先知，凡說預言的也都說到這些日</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">子。』（徒三：</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">24）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.15pt"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Meiryo,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">苦罪面前躬身反思</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:9.6pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">祭司的職分與先知的職分有何不同呢？祭司可以獻祭，而先知不可以。祭司也可代表神說話，好像亞倫。舊約記載祭司多次將神應許的福氣轉達給百姓，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">祭司是講祝福的話語。耶和華呼召撒母耳成為先知的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</div>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:5.15pt; margin-right:20.9pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">第一段話，記載在三：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">11-14，先知講話的內容，可</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">以講福氣，但舊約的先知多數是講神審判的話語。這次撒母耳如此隆重地被神呼召，由祭司變成先知，因為神要在以色列人中有一新的渠道，去同以色列民交往，神要藉着先知，宣佈審判會降臨以色列！所以先知都是人們討厭的，不是因為他們本身有甚麼不好，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">而是因為傳的就是審判的信息！</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.55pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">在以色列這段歷史開始時，神要先審判自己的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">子民</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">--</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">&nbsp; 這是先知職分的中心，像以利沙，以賽亞一樣，傳審判的福音。真假先知有甚麼分別呢，耶</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">二十三：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">16-19上告訴我們，假先知不停說，平安，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">平安，必沒有災禍臨到。但真先知就說，一定有災禍臨到！在撒母耳這麼關鍵的時刻，以色列人在舊約復</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">興的前夕，耶和華藉着先知講到神的審判臨格。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.5pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">原來耶和華的話語可以帶來福氣，也可以帶來災禍。今天教會只有感恩祈禱會，數算主恩，數算神一</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">路帶來的祝福。有甚麼聚會我們會聚在一起數算禍音</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">?難道二十一世紀的上帝只能給我們祝福，不能用災<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">難提醒我們？！為什麼我們不停地感謝上帝，但沒留意神可以藉着苦難提醒我們！？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.55pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.6pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">在美國「九一一」事件發生時，我們聽到基督教領袖在美國說，這次災難是因為美國人離開了上帝，我聽見了很不開心，你有何資格講這種話？後來我聽到在事件中，有弟兄那早剛要去世貿大廈上班，但忽</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">然肚子痛去不了，事後他在祈禱會分享感謝神救了</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">他。我不是說九一一是神的審判，但我們怎麼不夠膽去思考神有資格審判我們！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.6pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.6pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">難道我們只講福氣，不講禍音？難道基督教只講神保守我們一大覺睡到天亮，神保守我們上天堂，就平安了？神不可以審判我們個人和群體嗎？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:20.5pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">由撒母耳記到瑪拉基書，先知一直宣告，神有資格審判祂的子民，由王朝開始之前到王朝結束之</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">後，神的審判不停臨格以色列人當中，都是神自己的工作。沒錯，在約九講到耶穌醫好人之後，有人問耶穌，這人原來是瞎眼的，到底是他父母犯罪還是他自己犯罪。耶穌說，不是他們犯罪，而是為着顯出神的榮耀。但我們拿着這節聖經，就認定耶和華不能審判我們！請回看又一個神蹟之後，『後來耶穌在殿裏遇見他，對他說：你已經痊癒了；不要再犯罪，恐怕你遭遇的更加厲害。』（約五：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">14）。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.15pt"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Meiryo,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">清心準備聖靈臨格</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:9.6pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">徒五講述亞拿尼亞夫婦欺哄聖靈，立即死了。林前十一，保羅說教會裏的有些人領聖餐時沒有好好審查自己的罪，內中有人病了，有人死了，這些算不算</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">神的審判呢？舊約聖經一直延續到新約聖經，是講神</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">直到今日的工作中可以行審判。如果今天神讓你經歷</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">某些困難，有沒可能是神對你的提醒</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">?</span></span></span></span><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">我們今天不能</span></span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">隨便評論其他人，但我們卻可以反思：自己生命的遭</span></span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">遇，是否因着離開上帝，而得到神的提醒。</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-top:2.4pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-top:2.4pt; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">撒母耳被呼召成為先知，這告訴我們，神可以</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">在子民當中作提點的工作。神可以用我們的遭遇來提醒我們。我們來敬拜上帝時，不單止要感恩，還要自省：究竟在我們身上發生的事，是否因為我們在神前犯了罪？如果神將要復興一間教會，但因為一個人犯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">罪而不能復興，我們負不負得起這責任呢？亞干犯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">罪，神不能出手來拯救以色列人。在新約時代，我們期待溫馨的日子，但沒想到在和平的日子，神也審判犯罪的人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.4pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-right:21.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">神復興祂子民的時候，就是祂聖潔臨格之時</span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">，與此同時，也是祂審判之時。有何次神臨格而不帶着審</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">判？我們對伊甸園的光景羨慕不已，沒想到吃個果子</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">就被逐出了伊甸園。我們見過十災神奇妙的演繹後，正垂涎美麗迦南，沒想到真正進到迦南美地的老一代只有兩人。我們羨慕，大家在一起圍着圈唱歌唱聖詩慶祝復興（徒二至四），但原來有人向執事傳道人說</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">了謊就完了</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">! 每次神復興祂子民時，祂聖潔的要求就<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">在裏面！撒母耳記就是宣講神復興以色列國，先興起的不是皇帝，而是興起一個先知，去傳講神審判的信息。因為如果沒預備好，神的臨格就可能是災難。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.5pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.5pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">我們祈禱神來復興，你預備好了嗎？神的靈突然來到時，是審判抑或祝福？撒上三介紹先知的職分是審判的開始，再看第六章歸還約櫃時的事，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">19節『耶</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">和華因伯示麥人擅觀祂的約櫃，就擊殺了他們七十</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">人；那時有五萬人在那裏，百姓因耶和華大大擊殺他</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">們，就哀哭了。』這幫人不是外邦人，神聖潔的臨格</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">不是開玩笑的，不是輕輕鬆鬆的，別隨便說</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">: 聖靈有<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">空來坐坐吧。<strong>聖靈有時沒臨格，可能是恩待我們，給我們機會先悔改，</strong>之後我們才能敬拜獨一真神。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:21.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">撒母耳做先知為神講話，他經歷過以前的苦難，知道審判的重要，他親口對以色列全家講的第一句話是：『你們若一心歸順耶和華，就要把外邦的神和亞斯他錄從你們中間除掉，專心歸向耶和華，單單的事</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">奉祂。祂必救你們脫離非利士人的手。』（七<span style="letter-spacing:-.25pt">：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.25pt">3）</span></span></span></span><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">神的審判不是祂發脾氣的表達，而是祂慈愛的表達！</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:21.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">給我們機會回轉歸向耶穌，先知講禍音的同時，也告訴我們神已經在歷史再一次工作了！我們惟一可能的回應就是回轉歸向真神。我們不能看弟兄姊妹的遭遇下任何結論，因為聖經中有多位偉人的遭遇都是為義受逼迫。但我們自己知道自己，我們今天可能經歷的，是否是神給我們的多一次機會？！是否是神憐憫我們的表達？！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.15pt"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Meiryo,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">神賜人回轉的機會</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:9.65pt; margin-right:20.65pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">兩星期前，我在另一國家講道，認識一位牧師，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">成了朋友，還一齊去了賭場</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"> -- 不是去賭錢，只因他<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">有個事工是幫助賭場的人。他說他討厭「七」字，因他考會考了七次才合格，考車牌也考了七次！他年幼時已將生命奉獻給上帝，但不認真。第七次會考後，他開始讀書，考進有名的大學讀完碩士。人生暢順， </span><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">2003</span><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">年醫生突然對他說，你可能有癌症。時值「沙</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">士」，幾個月沒能就診，他天天困擾</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">&hellip;&hellip;。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.25pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-right:21.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">有一次他開車時，放一盒錄音帶聽着，剛好是培靈會信息，他聽後停車流着淚說，「神啊，祢一直呼喚我，我卻遲延至今，現在，我不知自己還有多少日子，但不管剩下多少，我奉獻給祢吧！」沙士結束後</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">檢查，不是癌症！但要實踐承諾，他便致攻讀進修，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">好在教會事奉。<strong>神往往在難處時提醒我們一些忽略了的事，是恩典抑或詛咒？我想，是恩典！</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.3pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">神給我們不同的經歷，可能是叫我們回來，是</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">恩典而不是詛咒！神今天怎樣在你的生命工作呢？是否有一個遭遇你不明白？這會不會是神恩典臨格的時候。我們願不願意回轉？有沒有些事你答應了神要去做，而至今沒有去做？這是回轉的機會。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">神在你的生命中有沒有這樣的提醒呢？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
				
				<br>
				<p class="h5">
					<span>講員：</span> 鮑維均牧師
					<br>
					<span>傳譯：</span> 周志豪牧師
				</p>			</div>
